{"type":"message","id":"0d5ae413","parentId":"c3b2f888","timestamp":"2026-04-08T08:45:48.011Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"明天（4月9日）上海的天气预计以多云为主，但夜晚可能会有阵雨。\n\n具体的温度区间大约在 **12°C 到 15°C** 之间。白天体感较为凉爽，建议出门记得带件外套，晚上如果出门的话，最好随身带把雨伞以防阵雨 🦊。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"vllm-8889","model":"gemma-4-31b-it","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775637944871,"responseId":"chatcmpl-85478ba8e7752566"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e7243e3e","parentId":"0d5ae413","timestamp":"2026-04-08T08:45:48.617Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 8th, 2026 - 16:45 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-08 08:45 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775637948613}}
